                      (          RRF.ASM):00054         *B0:READ FORMAT 0=SERIAL;1=BLOCK
                      (          RRF.ASM):00055         *B1:WRITE FORMAT 0=SERIAL;1=BLOCK
                      (          RRF.ASM):00056         *B2:XSFER RATE 0=ROM-RAM (1MSEC); 1=RAM-RAM (2 MSEC)
