                      (          RRF.ASM):00059         *B5:1=ODD FLAVOR
                      (          RRF.ASM):00060         *B6:1=B0-B3 WRITE SUPPRESS
                      (          RRF.ASM):00061         *B7:1=B4-B7 WRITE SUPPRESS
